Email NIDDK

Be sure to check out these pages before sending a question:

     * Frequently Asked Questions
     * Health Information
     * Customer Satisfaction Survey


   Please note: NIDDK will not provide medical advice.
   The medical information we provide is intended to help people better
   understand their health and their diagnosed disorders. For medical
   advice, diagnosis, and answers to your questions, NIDDK urges you to
   visit a qualified physician (or dietitian if your questions concern
   nutrition).

If you still want to send an email, please use the following form:


